Text: Grrrr...!!!

Damn it... It looks like we'll have to fight Lady
Delta after all...!

Trust Lady Alpha and Lady Gamma to do something like
this. As soon as they saw No. 93 fleeing, they sent
in their ultimate weapon.

This kind of decisiveness is a stark contrast to the
more sluggish moves of the Cult of Diablos...

Is this really the time to be smug? The situation...
is life-threatening!
Oh, Chi, you're always so dramatic.

You can afford to be calm because you know nothing
about it!
For starters, this whole labor dispute...

Shut up! You're all weak, so I'll take you all out
in one blow!
Huh?!
What?!
Woooshrrraaahhh!!! Moooooove!!!

Whaaaaaaat?!
Gwaaaaaaah?!

Grrr... You're better than golems, but you're still
too weak! Beta and Epsilon are way stronger!
U-Urrk... Unfortunately, it's all up to you now...
Wh-What...happened...?!

Tsk..! Just as I thought, Lady Delta's powers are
incredible! She's not just a step ahead—she's
leagues beyond us!
Lambda! You fight me, too!

...I cannot do that! Facing you head-on would most
definitely result in my death and defeat!
Therefore, we must resort to trickery!
Hehehe... Drown.
Huhhh?!
...Hmm? Nothing's happening.
...Impossible...!

Could it be that you...planned to collapse the floor
of the training grounds and plunge Lady Delta into
the abyss?

Yes, that was the plan, but...something's wrong.
I prepared this a long time ago, but it's
not activating...
Ahhh...
Heheheh! Give it up, Eta!

We've known about the modifications you secretly
made to the training center thanks to Lambda's
report!

I've disabled some of the defense systems in advance
to prevent them from being misused!

What...? When you put it that way, it sounds like
you're accusing me of espionage!
Laaambdaaa?

This... This is an enemy scheme! A plot to sow
discord! They're trying to fracture our unity and
cause our collapse from within!

Enough already! I don't understand what you're
saying, and I'm gonna take all of you down!

Hmph... We're having an important discussion here!
Quiet down for a moment, Delta.

I won't be quiet! Like Lady Alpha commanded,
I'll defeat everyone, but not kill them!
...If you want to play, then go play over there...
Lady Eta, what are you planning now—
Gyaahh?!
Gamma? Did you trip and fall again?

N-No...wait... How can I trip and fall when I wasn't
even moving—
Gamma... Dance.
Excuse me?!
Huh... Huhhh? Huuuhhh?!
M-My body! It's moving on its own!
Ooh... Gamma, you're quicker on your feet than usual!

And you're not falling at all! Wait, could you
actually move properly all this time?

Out of the Seven Shadows, Gamma isn't exactly the
most skilled at controlling slime...
So, it's easy to take control of hers...!
Aaaaahhhh?!

My slime is moving on its own! Is this a slime
sword—?! Wait, why does it feel sharper than usual?!
Now...dance...!
W-Waaaahhhh?!

Whoa! Why are you suddenly attacking me?! I'm your
ally!

N-No, it's not me doing this! My body, no, my slime
is moving on its own!!!

I don't really understand, but if you're gonna get
in my way, then it's time for you to sleep!
Owwwww!!! What's wrong with you, Delta?!

Whoa...! You're a tough one as usual! But I won't
lose either!
Save that talk for the enemy! I'm on your side!

You attacked me, your ally, so now you're the enemy!
Lady Alpha said to defeat the enemy!
You idioooot!!!
Hehehe... Let them fight among themselves...

Lady Eta...! How can you carry out such terrifying
acts so calmly...!

Matching Delta's attacks with Gamma's vitality to
neutralize each other... A sound strategy, Eta.

As for taking control of the slime and the slime
suit... I suppose whether it works or not depends on
the opponent.
Lady Alpha...!

The R&D department demands an increase in budget and
personnel...!
I cannot comply with your demands.
Then...I will seize it by force...
Try it if you can.

(...All the members have suddenly stopped fighting
to watch what Lady Eta and Lady Alpha do next...)
(Most likely, everyone here has realized the truth.)

(That the outcome of this battle will ultimately
come down to a showdown between Lady Eta and Lady
Alpha!)
